# OpenAI API 키 (서버 전용 — 이론 임베딩·해설 문구화)
# 일기 원문·생년월일은 AI로 전송하지 않습니다.
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here

# Supabase (일기·예보·이론 RAG 동기화)
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_supabase_anon_key

# 서버 전용 — RLS 우회. 절대 NEXT_PUBLIC_ 으로 노출하지 마세요.
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your_supabase_service_role_key

# 관리자 이메일 (쉼표 구분). 비어 있으면 /admin 전원 거부.
ADMIN_EMAILS=you@example.com

# --- Feature flags (Phase 1+, 기본 OFF — docs/FEATURE_FLAGS.md) ---
# NEXT_PUBLIC_FF_LEGACY_MENU=false
# NEXT_PUBLIC_FF_NEW_DIARY=false
# NEXT_PUBLIC_FF_PERSONALIZATION=false
# Phase 4 — 개인화 Ridge MVP (학습/표시 분리)
# NEXT_PUBLIC_FF_PERSONALIZATION_TRAIN=false
# NEXT_PUBLIC_FF_PERSONALIZATION_DISPLAY=false
# NEXT_PUBLIC_FF_NEW_ANALYSIS=false
# Phase 5 — 분석 UI·서술 (LLM/캐시 분리, 기본 OFF)
# NEXT_PUBLIC_FF_ANALYSIS_NARRATIVE_LLM=false
# FF_ANALYSIS_NARRATIVE_LLM=false
# NEXT_PUBLIC_FF_ANALYSIS_CACHE=false
# NEXT_PUBLIC_FF_SAJU_SNAPSHOT=false

# --- RLS cross-user verify (never commit; test accounts only) ---
# TEST_USER_A_EMAIL=rls-test-a@example.com
# TEST_USER_A_PASSWORD=
# TEST_USER_B_EMAIL=rls-test-b@example.com
# TEST_USER_B_PASSWORD=
# Optional fallback (prefer password above):
# TEST_USER_A_JWT=
# TEST_USER_B_JWT=
# docs/RLS_CROSS_USER_VERIFICATION.md
# node scripts/verify-rls-cross-user.mjs
#
# --- Phase 4 — 개인화 Ridge MVP remote verify ---
# Record counts BEFORE applying 010, then:
# BASELINE_DIARY_ENTRIES=2
# BASELINE_JOURNAL_ENTRIES=0
# BASELINE_ASTROLOGY_SNAPSHOTS=0
# docs/PHASE_4_REMOTE_VERIFICATION.md
# node scripts/verify-personalization-010.mjs
# node scripts/verify-rls-personalization-010.mjs
# node scripts/verify-personalization-training-e2e.mjs
#
# --- Phase 5 — 분석 UI·서술 remote / live verify ---
# Prefer TEST_USER_A/B; else JWT; else service role ephemeral users.
# node scripts/verify-analysis-remote-e2e.mjs
# FF_ANALYSIS_NARRATIVE_LLM=true node scripts/verify-analysis-narrative-live.mjs
# docs/PHASE_5_REMOTE_VERIFICATION.md
#
# --- Phase 6 — 최종 QA·출시 준비 ---
# node scripts/verify-phase6-release-gate.mjs
# docs/PHASE_6_FINAL_QA.md · docs/RELEASE_CHECKLIST.md
# docs/ENVIRONMENT_VARIABLES.md — never put TEST_USER_* in production
